{"date":"2003-12-03","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/aa/9d/91628_kLCwL.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/aa/9d/91628_kLCwL.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/aa/9d/91628_kLCwL.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/aa/9d/91628_kLCwL.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/aa/9d/91628_kLCwL.jpg"},"summary":"『インターステラ5555：THE 5TORY OF THE 5ECRET 5TAR 5YSTEM』とは、フランスのハウステクノデュオ：ダフト・パンクと松本零士とのコラボレーションによるアニメーションオペラ。\r\nかねてから松本のファンであったダフト・パンクの2人が自身のアルバム『ディスカバリー』の為に松本にビデオクリップの制作を依頼したのが始まり。\r\n少ない効果音以外は台詞は全くなく全編『ディスカバリー』の楽曲で構成されている67分のアニメーションである。\r\n2001年に単独のビデオクリップ（「ワン・モア・タイム」「エアロダイナミック」「デジタル・ラブ」「仕事は終わらない」）として公開されていたものを含め一連の作品として2003年に公開された。","name":"インターステラ5555:THE 5TORY OF THE 5ECRET 5TAR 5YSTEM","name_cn":"星际5555：异星梦系统秘传","tags":[{"name":"OVA","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003","count":47,"total_cont":0},{"name":"松本零士","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"daftpunk","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"東映アニメーション","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"东映","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"西尾大介","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"竹之内和久","count":11,"total_cont":0},{"name":"音乐","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立ova","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"东映动画","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SF","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"蠢朋克","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MV","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000-2009","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVAOAD特典","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Daft_Punk","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"辻田邦夫","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short_film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"心理","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2003年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"为我井克美","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原創","count":1,"total_cont":0},